瞧瞧我天火的英姿吧!
Behold to the only Jetfire!

2032
02:09:38,140 --> 02:09:41,800
现在让我给大家展示一下如何让敌人痛苦
Now let me show you how we brought them pain in my day.

2033
02:10:01,800 --> 02:10:03,180
我太老了
Too old for this crap.

2034
02:10:03,220 --> 02:10:04,260
继续前进
Keep going.

2035
02:10:04,260 --> 02:10:05,590
十五回合的战斗
15 minutes of fighting.

2036
02:10:25,760 --> 02:10:29,590
我就在大力神的下面
I am directly below the enemy's scrotum.

2037
02:10:30,340 --> 02:10:32,550
海平面上25.7米
25.7 metres above sea level,

2038
02:10:32,590 --> 02:10:33,760
北纬29.32度
29.32 north.

2039
02:10:33,760 --> 02:10:35,960
- 发射轨道 5-2
5点方向 - 目标锁定
- Field track, 5-2, 0500 o'clock. - Target acquired.

2040
02:10:36,050 --> 02:10:37,170
保持锁定 2号轨道
Killing track two.

2041
02:10:37,340 --> 02:10:39,170
锁定 发射
Lock. Fire.

2042
02:10:54,170 --> 02:10:56,130
太好了! 太好了!
Yeah! Yeah!

2043
02:10:56,170 --> 02:10:58,090
B1轰炸机 30秒后接近目标...
B-1, stand on my target. 30 seconds...

2044
02:10:59,880 --> 02:11:02,090
好的 我们现在必须转移了 明白吗?
We're gonna make a break for the beast on my command, okay?

2045
02:11:02,130 --> 02:11:04,000
你们两个就跟着我跑 明白吗?
You guys stick with me, you understand?

2046
02:11:04,040 --> 02:11:05,290
一步也不许离开
You stay on my ass.

2047
02:11:06,880 --> 02:11:08,750
希望那些F16能打准点
Hope these F-16s got good aim.

2048
02:11:08,750 --> 02:11:09,670
嗯 怎么了?
Yeah, why is that?

2049
02:11:10,090 --> 02:11:11,710
我告诉他们橘红色烟雾为打击目标
I told them to hit the orange smoke.

2050
02:11:13,540 --> 02:11:14,710
你是说橘红色的烟雾吗?
You mean that orange smoke?

2051
02:11:15,210 --> 02:11:16,960
这不是我扔的最好的一次 知道吗?
It wasn't my best toss, okay?

2052
02:11:18,670 --> 02:11:20,210
- 快跑!
- 快跑!
- Run! - Run!

2053
02:11:28,670 --> 02:11:30,210
来啦!
Incoming!

2054
02:11:33,330 --> 02:11:33,910
快点
Come on.

2055
02:12:08,040 --> 02:12:08,950
死吧!
Die!

2056
02:12:15,950 --> 02:12:17,280
山姆!
Sam!

2057
02:12:33,360 --> 02:12:35,200
别开火!
Hold your fire!

2058
02:12:37,410 --> 02:12:38,030
山姆!
Sam!

2059
02:12:40,110 --> 02:12:42,450
走开! 快去叫救护车
Get out! Get me an EVAC.

2060
02:12:44,450 --> 02:12:46,610
不能做点什么吗?
Can't you do something?

2061
02:13:21,730 --> 02:13:23,770
- 山姆! 山姆...
- 山姆!
- Sam! Sam... - Sam!

2062
02:13:30,480 --> 02:13:32,980
快点 我们走 我们走 快点!
Come on, we got to move. We got to move! Come on!

2063
02:13:38,110 --> 02:13:39,060
山姆!
Sammy!

2064
02:13:42,900 --> 02:13:46,350
准备! 电击 准备! 电击
Clear! Take a shot. Clear! Take a shot.

2065
02:13:46,440 --> 02:13:47,600
一 二 三
One, two, three.

2066
02:13:50,730 --> 02:13:51,350
别再这样
Do it again.

2067
02:13:57,190 --> 02:13:59,020
山姆!
Sam!

2068
02:14:00,850 --> 02:14:06,020
好了 听我的声音 我爱你 我需要你
Okay, listen to my voice. I love you and I need you.

2069
02:14:06,850 --> 02:14:12,180
拜托 拜托 为了我回来 山姆 拜托! 我爱你!
Please, please come back to me. Sam, please! I love you!

2070
02:14:23,970 --> 02:14:25,810
我死了吗?
Am I dead?

2071
02:14:26,600 --> 02:14:30,890
我们一直在关注你 很长 很长时间了
We have been watching you. A long, long time.

2072
02:14:33,180 --> 02:14:35,220
你为擎天柱而战斗
You have fought for Optimus,

2073
02:14:35,430 --> 02:14:39,890
我们唯一的后代 你英勇无畏 不怕牺牲
our last descendant, with courage and with sacrifice.

2074
02:14:39,930 --> 02:14:42,560
具有领袖精神
The virtues of a leader.

2075
02:14:43,010 --> 02:14:46,140
我们值得将秘密托付给你
A leader worthy of our secret.

2076
02:14:46,430 --> 02:14:49,350
原能矩阵不是被发现的
The Matrix of Leadership is not found.

2077
02:14:49,890 --> 02:14:51,300
而是通过努力得来的
It is earned.

2078
02:14:52,390 --> 02:14:54,680
回到擎天柱身边
Return now to Optimus,

2079
02:14:55,300 --> 02:14:57,550
将他的火种源融合到原能矩阵中
merge the Matrix with his Spark.

2080
02:14:58,220 --> 02:15:02,930
那是你此生注定的命运
It is, and always has been, your destiny.

2081
02:15:07,720 --> 02:15:08,720
山姆
Sam.

2082
02:15:15,090 --> 02:15:16,420
我爱你
I love you.

2083
02:15:55,290 --> 02:15:58,210
孩子 你为我而回来
Boy, you returned for me.

2084
02:15:59,670 --> 02:16:01,670
活着的超级领袖!
A living Prime!

2085
02:16:03,210 --> 02:16:05,630
简直不敢相信
I don't believe it.

2086
02:16:15,830 --> 02:16:18,210
我的原能矩阵
My Matrix.

2087
02:16:23,710 --> 02:16:25,000
站起来 站起来 站起来 站起来
Get up, get up, get up, get up.

2088
02:16:26,210 --> 02:16:27,500
站起来 擎天柱!
Get up, Prime!

2089
02:16:29,290 --> 02:16:32,790
- 哦 不
- 他要摧毁太阳
- Oh, no. - He's turned on the machine.

2090
02:16:33,580 --> 02:16:35,290
你要阻止他 站起来!
You gotta stop him. Get up!

2091
02:16:35,620 --> 02:16:37,160
擎天柱!
Optimus!

2092
02:16:39,290 --> 02:16:41,750
堕落金刚 我的主人
Fallen, my master.

2093
02:16:41,910 --> 02:16:46,250
其他那些超级领袖都不能阻挡我
My brothers could not stop me from this.

2094
02:16:47,250 --> 02:16:51,830
- 对
- 现在 太阳是我的了
- Yes. - Now I claim your sun.

2095
02:16:54,660 --> 02:16:56,370
向金字塔顶射击
Enemy target, top of pyramid.

2096
02:16:56,370 --> 02:16:58,490
行动 行动 行动
Engage, engage, engage.

2097
02:17:03,870 --> 02:17:06,780
很快 我们的力量会更强大
In moments, we'll be at siren strength.

2098
02:17:22,610 --> 02:17:27,070
我当霸天虎的日子里 今天才真正做了件值得做的事情
I never did a thing worth doing until now.

2099
02:17:27,740 --> 02:17:30,530
擎天柱 收下我的礼物
Optimus, take my parts.

2100
02:17:30,740 --> 02:17:33,660
这能量之强大 你无法预料
And you'll have a power you've never known.

2101
02:17:34,570 --> 02:17:36,740
请完成你的使命
Fulfill your destiny.

2102
02:17:42,780 --> 02:17:45,030
汽车人 通电!
Jolt, electrify!

2103
02:17:45,330 --> 02:17:47,330
移植加力燃烧器

2104
02:18:05,610 --> 02:18:07,280
出击
Let's roll.

2105
02:18:09,730 --> 02:18:11,610
开火 瞄准金字塔!
Fire. Take it off to the pyramid!

2106
02:18:23,650 --> 02:18:27,320
这个星球将永远陷入黑暗中
This planet will be dark forever.

2107
02:18:49,650 --> 02:18:51,900
和你的兄弟们一样去死
Die like your brother.

2108
02:18:52,520 --> 02:18:54,810
他们也是你的兄弟
They were your brothers too.

2109
02:19:23,470 --> 02:19:25,770
红蜘蛛...
First gra...

2110
02:19:38,640 --> 02:19:40,720
你选错了目标!
You picked the wrong planet!

2111
02:19:43,640 --> 02:19:45,640
拿下你的面罩
Give me your face.

2112
02:19:54,140 --> 02:19:58,260
我赢了 你失败了
I rise. You fall.

2113
02:20:00,340 --> 02:20:03,550
不 不
No. No.

2114
02:20:05,050 --> 02:20:09,760
我不想劝你做胆小鬼 主人 但有时侯
Not to call you a coward, Master, but sometimes,

2115
02:20:09,760 --> 02:20:13,510
胆小鬼往往能生存下来
cowards do survive.

2116
02:20:14,050 --> 02:20:15,970
这不算完
This isn't over.

2117
02:20:43,420 --> 02:20:46,250
经历了这一切你才愿意说你爱我
You took all of this for you to tell me that you love me.

2118
02:20:47,960 --> 02:20:49,460
你先说的
You said it first.

2119
02:21:40,870 --> 02:21:43,290
谢谢你 山姆 你救了我的命
Thank you, Sam, for saving my life.

2120
02:21:44,750 --> 02:21:45,330
别客气
You're welcome.

2121
02:21:46,790 --> 02:21:48,540
谢谢你信任我
Thank you for believing in me.

2122
02:21:53,240 --> 02:21:57,910
我们的种族因为被遗忘的过去而走到一起
Our races united by a history long forgotten.

2123
02:21:57,910 --> 02:22:01,200
齐心协力面对未来
And a future we shall face together.

2124
02:22:01,910 --> 02:22:06,200
我是擎天柱 在此发出倡议
I am Optimus Prime, and I send this message

2125
02:22:06,240 --> 02:22:09,450
让这段历史流传下去
so that our past will always be remembered.

2126
02:22:09,450 --> 02:22:13,530
我们拥有珍贵的记忆 生生不息
For in those memories, we live on.

