2129
02:22:36,260 --> 02:22:39,320
很高兴你能来听课 爱因斯坦教授
So glad you can join us, Professoer Einstein.

2130
02:22:40,180 --> 02:22:41,330
对 最近有点忙
Yeah, I was kind of busy.

2131
